name: The Thrill Is Gone
comments: This song closed out the 2010 edition of the Eric Clapton Guitar Festival at Toyota Park in Bridgeville, Illinois. It was an eleven minute extended version that was mostly instrumental.  For the majority of the song it featured five guitarists, B.B. King, Eric Clapton, Jimmie Vaughan, Robert Cray and Joe Bonamassa.  Toward the end of the song all of the performers at the Festival came on stage and started playing the song.
